content.rendered:
Directed by Shiva Raj Kanumuri.

Written by Rahul Ramakrishna.

Cast Krishna Murali Posani. Rahul Ramakrishna(Yadagiri). Srinivasa Reddy((as Srinivas Reddy)). Meesam Suresh(Clark). Sree Vishnu(Kantha Rao) . (0)

Language Telugu.

Producers Kandagatla Bhaskar. Shiva Raj Kanumuri.

Production Shiva Raj Films.
